    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesnt feel like i'm fighting though. it feels more like i'm just drowning in the same water every single time. no matter how much i struggle to stay afloat, i just sink back down to the bottom. it's just... it's exhausting. i feel like there's no point in even trying to fix things anymore if the result is always the same.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
